{
  "stem": "512.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, when they took us in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, number one, it was a horrible, horrible fear when you saw them, even.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were spic and span in their boots and terrifying, absolutely shivering, shivering.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, you know, we already knew so much about Nazis and all that because we were aware of everything what was going on in the world and what Hitler has done, so horrible, horrible fear, and also seeing people being beaten because they, unfortunately, had nervous breakdowns.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't know they were yelling, and they were screaming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they, they-- so instead of-- but eventually, they were taken away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And questions, you never asked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, there were whispers and things, but you didn't ask any questions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anybody didn't dare.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So then also the Nazis started to give up everything that you have there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because my father came home, and he told us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember the words-- you know, those were all very foreign words-- that the earth is moving, that some people in the Ukraines were, were-- dug their own graves and thrown in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some were still alive, and they were shoved with the earth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So all those stories were terribly, terribly terrifying to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were terrifying even at home because you were attacked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if, if a cat ran by the house or a, or a bird or something, you always feared, they're breaking in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All those things, it was a horrible, horrible fear on all of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- but we were-- we knew that the Nazis, what they were doing in, in [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Poland because Poland, they started persecuting them much earlier than us.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
